= Scrolling Credits display
Simple vertical scrolling text display with fading at the edges.


This is a sample application using Ruby/GNOME2, Ruby/GnomeCanvas.

{{image_right('gnomecanvas-credits-snapshot1.png')}}
== Download
* {{attach_anchor('gnomecanvas-credits.rb')}}

== Requirements
Developed environments are:
* ruby 1.8.1 (2003-12-25) [i686-linux]
* Ruby-GNOME2-0.9.0(Ruby/GTK2, Ruby/GnomeCanvas)

== Usage
$ ruby gnomecanvas-credits.rb

